Package: arraydm
Type: Package
Title: AGRF Differential Methylation Analysis Package
Version: 0.1
Date: 07/08/2020
Author: Lesley Gray <lesley.gray@agrf.org.au>
Maintainer: Lesley Gray <lesley.gray@agrf.org.au>
Description: Provides functions for analysis of methylation array data. 
